text: John Morris (5 June 1831 - 9 December 1921) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1858/59. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1831 births Category:1921 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: John Morris (Australian cricketer)
